{"lemma":"غَرَقُ","slug":"غَرَقُ","root":"غ.ر.ق","root_slug":"غ-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غَرَق","root":"غرق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31714","","n31721"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to drown","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"drowning","examples":[{"text":"حَتَّىٰۤ إِذَاۤ أَدۡرَكَهُ ٱلۡغَرَقُ قَالَ ءَامَنتُ أَنَّهُۥ لَاۤ إِلَـٰهَ إِلَّا ٱلَّذِيۤ ءَامَنَتۡ بِهِۦ بَنُوۤا۟ إِسۡرَ ٰ⁠ۤءِيلَ وَأَنَا۠ مِنَ ٱلۡمُسۡلِمِينَ"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to drown (someone or something)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣa.ri.qa/","/ʁɪrəɡ/","/ɣar.raq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31714","headword_ar":"غَرِقَ","root":"grq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaqN","text_ar":"غَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAra","text_ar":"غَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasaba","text_ar":"رَسَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlmaA='i","text_ar":"فِى المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the water"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Mgh, O, Msb:) primarily ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he drowned;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sank under water, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the water entered the two apertures of his nose so that it filled its passages and he died."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqa fiY AlbilaAdi","text_ar":"غَرِقَ فِى البِلَادِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, *"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went downwards and disappeared"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasaba","text_ar":"رَسَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the lands,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tracts of land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaqa","text_ar":"غَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (thus in the O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqa","text_ar":"غَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (thus accord. to the K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drank a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"draught such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guroqap","text_ar":"غُرْقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, K:) so says IAar. (O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaqotu mina All~abani","text_ar":"غَرَقْتُ مِنَ اللَّبَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, and thus in copies of the K, in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqotu","text_ar":"غَرِقْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaqotu","text_ar":"غَرَقْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina All~abani guroqapF","text_ar":"مِنَ اللَّبَنِ غُرْقَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I took a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"draught such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuvobap","text_ar":"كُثْبَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) so says Ibn-'Abbád. (O, TA.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqa","text_ar":"غَرِقَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, without want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoqFA","text_ar":"غَرْقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_igoraAqFA","text_ar":"اـِغْرَاقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", see under 4."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31721","headword_ar":"غَرِقٌ","root":"grq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAriqN","text_ar":"غَارِقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariyqN","text_ar":"غَرِيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"part. ns. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqa","text_ar":"غَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K,) the first and second signifying ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Drowning;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sinking in water without dying;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb;) and the third, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drowned;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dead by sinking in water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kh, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugoraqN","text_ar":"مُغْرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugar~aqN","text_ar":"مُغَرَّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (so in different copies of the S;) and accord. to the Bari', the third may have both meanings agreeably with analogy; (Msb;) [see an instance of its usage in the former sense voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagamogama","text_ar":"تَغَمْغَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the first is sometimes used in the latter sense; for] it is said in a trad. that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariq","text_ar":"غَرِق"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of those who are [reckoned as]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uhadaA='","text_ar":"شُهَدَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or martyrs: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahiydN","text_ar":"شَهِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (O, TA;) though it is said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqN","text_ar":"غَرِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sinking in water"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like as does"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAriqN","text_ar":"غَارِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariyqN","text_ar":"غَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dead therein;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to Aboo-'Adnán"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqN","text_ar":"غَرِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overcome by the water but not having yet sunk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariyqN","text_ar":"غَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having sunk"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariyqN","text_ar":"غَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoqaY","text_ar":"غَرْقَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, O, Msb, K. *) ―         -b2-  It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA^otiY EalaY Aln~aAsi zamaAnN","text_ar":"يَاْتِى عَلَى النَّاسِ زَمَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yanojuw fiyhi A^aHadN A_il~aA mano daEaA duEaA='a Algariqi","text_ar":"لَا يَنْجُو فِيهِ اَحَدٌ اـِلَّا مَنْ دَعَا دُعَا=ءَ الغَرِقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A time will come upon men in which no one will become safe but he who prays with the praying of the drowning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; app. meaning, but he who is sincere in praying, as is he who is on the brink of destruction. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAta gariqFA fiY Alxamori","text_ar":"مَاتَ غَرِقًا فِى الخَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in another trad., means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He died going to the utmost point,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"degree, in the drinking of wine."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN gariqapN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ غَرِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land in the utmost state of irrigation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IF, A, O, K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqN","text_ar":"غَرِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariyqN","text_ar":"غَرِيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signify (tropical:)  A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deeply"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in debt:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overwhelmed by trials."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu lagariqu AlS~awoti","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَغَرِقُ الصَّوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is frightened so that his voice is stopped short."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn- 'Abbád, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","TA"]}]}}